response.overview: Mother and daughter bicker over everything -- what Anna wears, whom she likes and what she wants to do when she's older. In turn, Anna detests Tess's fiancé. When a magical fortune cookie switches their personalities, they each get a peek at how the other person feels, thinks and lives.
response.tagline: Mondays are manic. Wednesdays are wild. And Fridays are about to get a little freaky.
response.title: Freaky Friday
